        <num>CC 728</num>
        <heading>728.  Limitation of use</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 728.  Limitation of use.
The use of a predial servitude may be limited to certain times.  Thus, the rights of drawing water and of passage may be confined to designated hours.</p>
        </content>
